The soulfire within bursts into blue particles
and enters the bodies of all four of you.
You are now immune to the
An ancient structure that has been standing in the
Blazing Sands for as long as anyone can remember.
It's filled with the lost souls of travelers
who have died seeking riches in here, only
to be lost in its twisting hallways.
Any sort of light-related abilities are a must
in here, as the lost souls that lurk within
do not like the feel of holy brightness.
Powerful equipment lies in here that allows
adventurers to see the lost souls with
their own eyes... it would be ill-advised
to not seek this equipment out.
However, if you don't have it, your only hope
is to stay out of sight of the lost souls.
Going further in unprepared may very well be the
end of you! Proceed with caution!
